# Keep host build artifacts OUT of the image build context (WS15-T3): every dist/ the
# runtime needs is built inside the image (apps/worker/Dockerfile build stage), so a stale
# host dist can never be silently baked in — that's how a staging image once shipped a
# pre-fix @receipts/venues build over freshly-merged source.
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
.git
.next
**/.next
